OL,3,C"Soul destroying" blazes in the
OL,4,CMournes says Minister after weekend of
OL,5,Cwildfires
OL,7,FStormont's agriculture minister has
OL,8,Fsaid wildfires in the Mourne Mountains
OL,9,Fare "soul-destroying" as firefighters
OL,10,Fcontinued to monitor the situation on
OL,11,FMonday morning.
OL,13,FMore than 50 firefighters battled
OL,14,Fblazes over the weekend in a number of
OL,15,Fareas across the range, as hot and dry
OL,16,Fweather continued.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@UO]
