OL,3,C"Soul destroying" blazes in the
OL,4,CMournes says Minister after weekend of
OL,5,Cwildfires
OL,7,FOn Sunday the Northern Ireland Fire &
OL,8,FRescue Service (NIFRS) spokesperson
OL,9,Fsaid crews "are currently dealing with
OL,10,Fa number of wildland fires in the
OL,11,FBallagh Road, Newcastle and Sandbank
OL,12,FRoad, Hilltown areas of the Mourne
OL,13,FMountains".
OL,15,FThey added: "Hill walkers and locals
OL,16,Fare requested to avoid the area due to
OL,17,Ffire risk, heavy smoke and to help
OL,18,Fsupport firefighting operations. NIFRS
OL,19,Frequest the public act responsibly if
OL,20,Fyou are in the countryside this
OL,21,Fweekend."
OL,26,@qD@LOUuD@JO]wD@MOU}D@IO]
