OL,3,C"Soul destroying" blazes in the
OL,4,CMournes says Minister after weekend of
OL,5,Cwildfires
OL,7,FDaera minister Andrew Muir described
OL,8,Fthe Mourne wildfires as "soul-
OL,9,Fdestroying".
OL,11,F"The impact of these fires is real and
OL,12,Fsignificant, with lives potentially at
OL,13,Frisk, communities in fear and natural
OL,14,Fhabitats destroyed," he said.
OL,16,F"I am immensely grateful to the NI
OL,17,FFire and Rescue Service for the
OL,18,Fsustained response in challenging
OL,19,Fconditions and would urge everyone to
OL,20,Fheed calls to stay away whilst
OL,21,Ffirefighting continues."
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@KO]sD@AOUvD@TO]xD@AOU}D@XO]
