OL,3,C"Soul destroying" blazes in the
OL,4,CMournes says Minister after weekend of
OL,5,Cwildfires
OL,7,FSinn Fein MP for South Down Chris
OL,8,FHazzard said firefighters had "shown
OL,9,Fincredible bravery and dedication,
OL,10,Fworking in difficult conditions to
OL,11,Fprotect the heart of the Mournes".
OL,13,F"These mountains are a precious
OL,14,Fnatural resource and a site of immense
OL,15,Fbeauty, and it is devastating to see
OL,16,Fhectares of vegetation destroyed by
OL,17,Ffire yet again," he said.
OL,26,@pD@_OUsD@aO]uD@AOUyD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
