OL,3,C"Soul destroying" blazes in the
OL,4,CMournes says Minister after weekend of
OL,5,Cwildfires
OL,7,FHe added: "This incident serves as a
OL,8,Fstark reminder of how vulnerable our
OL,9,Flandscape is during these periods. I
OL,10,Furge everyone to be extremely careful
OL,11,Fand vigilant while the current weather
OL,12,Fwarnings remain in effect to prevent
OL,13,Ffurther damage to our environment and
OL,14,Fany risk to life."
OL,26,@oD@KOUvD@RO]
